{"tid":1492951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續為你報時 現時係2019年8月21日 下午13時05分","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:17:10.000Z","uid":131782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86d53e183e7b69039ca3dc7a18ebfd2aacbd2801","tid":1492951,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得一個月前嘅元朗發生咩事呢<br />\n<br />\n如果唔記得嘅 我提一提你 <br />\n<br />\n一個月前 721當晚<br />\n<br />\n元朗有一單白衣人無差別攻擊市民嘅恐怖襲擊<br />\n<br />\n受襲者當中包括記者 市民 街坊 孕婦<br />\n有人甚至被打到血流滿面<br />\n<br />\n而警方係所有人受襲後39分鐘才到場<br />\n及後更當著全球700萬人面前講大話<br />\n聲稱係現場見不到有施襲者手持武器<br />\n<br />\n事始至今 當天的施襲者未有一人被起訴<br />\n<br />\n請問大家 政府一直強調香港擁有的司法制度在那？<br />\n<br />\n你還要盲撐 還要沉默嗎？<br />\n<br />\n希望今天晚上7時正可在元朗西鐵站見到大家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wh7HOP3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwh7HOP3.jpg&h=9477ca8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8a5utP4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8a5utP4.png&h=ec416329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1H8KoW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1H8KoW.gif&h=415d9ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d4b906ec4b869e302cff81a8e70c465fb1325c6","tid":1492951,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=